description:
These TanglePANDAs are a personal appreciation for the recipient.  
Each of them is important to the IOTA ecosystem. 

Exactly 18 personalized NFTs are currently available as a non-public special collection outside of the normal TanglePANDAs range.

NOTE: After the collection has been published, the individual NFTs are finally personalized and released.
name: TanglePANDAs Giveaway
